title: FRONT MISSION EVOLVED - Xbox 360 [Region Free]
description:
Front Mission Evolved  is a third-person shooter video game developed by Double Helix Games and published by Square Enix. Unlike previous Front Mission titles which a tactical role-playing game structure, players engage in combat in real time on 3D maps using giant robotic weapons of war known as mechs. The game also features a single player story mode and several multiplayer combat modes with up to eight players.

The game features a story reboot of the Front Mission series and deals with the rising tensions in the late 22nd century between global powers utilizing orbital elevators to expand their reach into space.

Developer(s) 	Double Helix Games
Publisher(s) 	Square Enix
Producer(s) 	Shinji Hashimoto
Designer(s) 	David O. Hall
